;"low servant"
:Either based on the northern foreigners' endo-ethnonym, or more likely {{der|zh|aav}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Compare {{w|Monic languages|Proto-Monic}} *'''ɗiik''', {{w|Bahanaric languages|Proto-Bahnaric}} *'''ɗɨc''', as well as {{cog|mkh-pro|**ɗiək ~ ɗiik ~ *ɗik||slave}}.
